Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: Flask-YunPian
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Flask extension for YunPian API
Home-page: https://github.com/codeif/Flask-YunPian
Author: codeif
Author-email: me@codeif.com
License: MIT
Description: Flask-YunPian
        =============
        
        云片_发送短信的Flask扩展
        
        使用
        ----
        
        .. code-block::
        
            from flask_yunpin import YunPian
        
            yunpian = YunPian()
            yunpian.init_app(app)
        
        
        发送短信
        --------
        
        .. code::
        
            yunpian.send(phones, content, sign=None)
        
        phones可以传单个手机号或者手机号列表，分别调用单条发送接口和批量发送接口
        
        
        配置项
        ------
        
        ======================  ====================================
        YUNPIAN_APIKEY          apikey
        YUNPIAN_DEFAULT_SIGN    默认签名, 例如: 招商银行， 不包含【】
        ======================  ====================================
        
        
        .. 云片： https://www.yunpian.com/
        
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
